[person]person_101|[underline]Ambrosio[/underline][/person]. You make man in his early
or first created state as savage
like those that now inhabit [place]place_685|New-[line]Holland[/place] or [place]place_1160|New Zealand[/place] acquiring
by the little use that they make
of a feeble reason the power of
