he now exists can only be raised with
great care & difficulty from the in-
-fant to the mature state, all his

[page]22|MS-DAVY-11404-000-00022|dnp14d020pp|92018656[/page]
motions are at first automatic
and become voluntary by association
he has to learn every thing by slow
and difficult processes, many months
